---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | LeavingAmerica.co"
  description="Privacy Policy for LeavingAmerica.co. How we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our free tools for Americans living abroad."
>
<div class="ip-page">

  <div class="ip-header">
    <div class="ip-wrap">
      <span class="ip-label">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="ip-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="ip-lead">LeavingAmerica.co operates the website leavingamerica.co. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our free tools and content, including the Salary Arbitrage Calculator, Country Match quiz, Retire Abroad Calculator, and Expat Tax Guide.</p>
      <p class="ip-date">Last updated: June 17, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ip-body">
    <div class="ip-wrap">

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect information in the following ways:</p>

<h3>Information you provide directly</h3>
<p>When you use our tools (Salary Arbitrage Calculator, Country Match quiz, Retire Abroad Calculator), you may enter information such as your US city, annual income, savings amount, or personal preferences. We do not store this information on our servers. All calculations run in your browser.</p>

<h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
<p>When you visit our website, we automatically collect certain information through cookies and similar tracking technologies, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Browser type and version</li>
<li>Pages you visit and time spent on each page</li>
<li>Referring website or search query</li>
<li>Device type and operating system</li>
<li>Approximate geographic location derived from IP address (typically country or region level)</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
<ul>
<li>Operate and improve our website</li>
<li>Understand how visitors use our tools</li>
<li>Display relevant advertisements through Google AdSense</li>
<li>Analyze traffic through Google Analytics</li>
<li>Detect and prevent fraud or abuse</li>
</ul>

<h2>Cookies</h2>
<p>We use cookies and similar technologies to operate our website and serve relevant ads. Cookies are small text files stored on your device. We use the following types of cookies:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for the website to function, including storing your calculator session data temporarily.</li>
<li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Used by Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our website.</li>
<li><strong>Advertising cookies:</strong> Used by Google AdSense to show relevant advertisements based on your interests.</li>
</ul>
<p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect some website functionality.</p>
<p>Where required by law, visitors may be asked to consent to non-essential cookies before they are set.</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We use the following third-party services that may collect information about you:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Web analytics service used to understand how visitors interact with our website. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
<li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> Advertising service used to display relevant ads. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
<li><strong>World Bank API:</strong> Used to retrieve public economic data. No personal information is transmitted.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
<p>Some links on this website are affiliate links. If you purchase a product or service through those links, we may receive a commission at no additional cost to you. These third parties have their own privacy policies which govern how they handle your data.</p>

<h2>Data Retention</h2>
<p>We do not store personal data on our servers. Salary Arbitrage calculator inputs are processed locally in your browser and are not transmitted to us. Analytics data is retained by Google according to their data retention policies.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>While LeavingAmerica.co does not store personal data provided through the calculator, visitors may have privacy rights relating to information collected by third-party services used on this website.</p>
<p>Requests relating to data collected by LeavingAmerica.co may be directed to <a href="mailto:contact@leavingamerica.co">contact@leavingamerica.co</a>.</p>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>Our website is not directed at children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

<h2>International Visitors</h2>
<p>LeavingAmerica.co is operated internationally and may be accessed from different countries. Information collected by third-party services used on this website may be processed in jurisdictions outside your country of residence.</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:<br>
<a href="mailto:contact@leavingamerica.co">contact@leavingamerica.co</a></p>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>
</BaseLayout>
